channel.title: Comments on: Last weekend in Tretes

item.title: By: Auntie Phyllis
item.dc:creator: Auntie Phyllis
item.description: I am so jealous, I would love to be u. Keep up the blog, it is almost like being there. I know the country must be really beatiful. We miss u but live vicariously through ur blogs. Love from me and kimmie

item.title: By: Will Sanders
item.dc:creator: Will Sanders
item.description: Thank you to who ever put up that photo, I must have been sleeping at the wheel to not see Godzilla when I first took the picture. That is the funny thing about Indonesia, we see Godzilla so often that we don't even really notice anymore. That's just how cool we are.
item.content:encoded: Thank you to who ever put up that photo, I must have been sleeping at the wheel to not see Godzilla when I first took the picture. That is the funny thing about Indonesia, we see Godzilla so often that we don’t even really notice anymore. That’s just how cool we are.

item.title: By: Will Sanders
item.dc:creator: Will Sanders
item.description: Yeah, I really liked talking to you guys too. I miss you guys a whole bunch but not as bad as China because I still get to hang out with nice people a lot here. But talking to you guys the other night made me pine for late nights over beers at your house, conversations about Stan Lee at 4 AM, and all that. Thanks for being blog believer #1
